body_html: The tf.contrib.data.rejection_resample() transformation allows you to specify a mapping from Dataset elements to an integer class, and a vector of probabilities representing the target distribution (indexed by class) for the resampling. Can you be more specific about what a Dataset.resample() method would do in addition to this?
